Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我必須竭盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將自己現在力所能及之事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Smash
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有之前那麼痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是盲目地使用蠻力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是只將力量集中在指尖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然超越了700米!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於有個像點英雄的記錄了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的手指都腫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入學考試的時候也是這樣 真是奇怪的「個性」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…那股力量是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人的「個性」毫無例外都在4歲覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這的確…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人對我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說我一定可以成為英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還說這是我贏得的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快給我解釋清楚 廢久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 這張布條…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是由碳素纖維和特殊合金鋼線製成的束縛武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要三番四次都讓我使用「個性」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有乾眼症
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然「個性」很厲害 但是這也太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雄英高中1-A班 班主任 相澤消太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠消除視野內敵人的「個性」 眨一眼就會解除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要浪費時間 下一個快做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手指沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前還只是路邊那個毫不起眼的小石子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小勝真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的「個性」好帥氣 不知道我什麼時候才能覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管廢久有什麼樣的「個性」 反正沒我的好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是路邊毫不起眼的小石子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn方正粗圆_GBK\pos(424,350)\fs41\bord2\xshad-5\alpha&H00&\1c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H000000&}第6話 {\r\b1\fn方正粗圆_GBK\pos(424,350)\fs41\bord2\xshad-5\alpha&H00&\1c&H1600CB&\4c&H000000&}奮鬥吧 書呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,380)\fs39\fsp5\bord3}仰臥起坐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後 在和疼痛鬥爭的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(427,380)\fs39\fsp5\bord3}坐位體前屈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於完成了體力測試的所有科目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,46)\fs39\fsp5\bord3}耐力跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我趕緊來公布大家的成績
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總分就是單純的各科目的累計分數
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口頭說明太費時間 我會全部公布出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總分排名最後的同學將被勒令退學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能拿得出手的記錄也只有投球記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後面的耐力跑也因為痛感太強 成績也不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排名最末尾的人會被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勒令退學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,補充一句 勒令退學是騙你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了挖掘你們的「個性」潛能的一個善意謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種東西肯定是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微動點腦子都知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有發現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有點被嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論何時我都會奮戰到底的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,測試結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教室裡有課表之類的書本 大家回去記得看一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綠谷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去保健室讓老婆婆給你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從明天開始還有更加殘酷的測試等著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之算是闖過了這一關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過對我而言能做到的事還太少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從最末尾開始努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從此開始 我還要繼續學習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了更加接近自己憧憬的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相澤你這個大騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歐爾麥特先生 你都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很空閒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善意的謊言?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚人節早在一週前就過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年你將高一的一整個班的所有成員都勒令退學了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要判斷他們沒有前途就狠心將其拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種男人居然會撤回自己的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也在那個孩子身上看到了可能性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真看好他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對一名老師來說 這樣不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是認為他的可能性不是零
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有前途的人 我什麼時候都會拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼事情比半吊子地追尋夢想更要殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也算是你的溫柔吧 相澤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然還是跟你合不來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累趴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飯田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手指好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多虧了Recovery Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好神奇 治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是感覺身體更累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的「個性」只能增強人們的治癒能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治癒也是需要消耗體力的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果持續受到大面積傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會消耗更多的體力 反而導致死亡要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而導致死亡!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能每次都依靠別人的救助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須儘快變得能夠調控自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我真是太佩服相澤老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本以為這是高中英雄教學的最高學府
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到教師居然會用謊言來激勵學生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初以為飯田是個可怕的人 原來只是為人認真而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個是去車站嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗日同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是無限女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是麗日御茶子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是飯田天哉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有你是綠谷…木偶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木偶!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為體力測試的時候 爆豪是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廢久 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,437)\fs21}deku
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼叫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我的真名是出久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廢久 是小勝拿我尋開心才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蔑稱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是木偶聽上去像是加油的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(302,437)\fs21}deku
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請叫我木偶!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綠谷!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太衝動了吧 那是蔑稱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是哥白尼式的展開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥白?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然還有很多我無法做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此我必須奮發圖強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 歐爾麥特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於交到朋友這件事 我還是可以感到開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在可不是掉以輕心的時候 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從明天開始才是正劇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雄英高中英雄科的課表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上午是必修課 英語之類的普通課程
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誰知道這些英文句子哪裡錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好普通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無聊透頂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Everybody heads up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出你們的熱情來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關係代詞的位置錯了 所以是第四個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.31,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 八百萬 Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午在大食堂能吃到美味廉價的午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是米飯最王道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:09:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超安心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後是下午的課堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄基礎學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很普通地從門進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是歐爾麥特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 真的來當老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他穿的是白銀時代的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}註：白銀時代指超級英雄在美國主流漫畫界成為潮流的時代。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畫風太與眾不同 都起雞皮疙瘩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我負責的科目是英雄基礎學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是一門通過各種英雄來塑造英雄基礎的科目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學分也是所有科目中最高的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼馬上開始的就是這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,訓練…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有和它一起的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據你們入學前上交的「個性」介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和未來期望而製成的英雄服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換好衣服之後 按次序到操場β集合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs21\fad(200,200)}My hero
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs21\fad(200,200)}You always show me what I gotta do
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs21\fad(200,200)}I made up my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs21\fad(200,200)}I wanna be like you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs21\fad(200,200)}Sometimes anything doesn't go well
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs21\fad(200,200)}I do believe what I'm workin'on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs21\fad(200,200)}Do or do not just keep running
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外表也是很重要的 少年少女們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今天開始  你們要認識到…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 大家看上去都很帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 讓我們開始吧 受精卵們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服裝設計
Dialogue: 2,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在入學之前 學生需要提交
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.52,0:11:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「個性」介紹 身體信息 設計圖等具體要求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 2,0:11:59.40,0:12:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校專屬的贊助公司就能為我們配備最先端的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是非常人性化的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
